            <h2>CONNECTIONS OBJECTIVES</h2>
            <div>Throughout the Connections course, you should think about the reason you are engaging in the college experience. The objective of Connections is that at the end of the course you can comfortably answer all three of the big questions below, and that you better understand the university and your place within it. Each activity, assignment, workshop, and discussion at Connections is designed to help answer one of the three big questions.</div>
