        <div id="section2P" class="section2">
            <h2>CLASSROOM CIVILITY</h2>
                <div class="details">
                    <div class="description">
                        <div class="editableHtml">
                            <p>Regardless of intent, careless or ignorant remarks can be very offensive and detrimental to others. If you feel uncomfortable in a classroom due to offensive language or actions by an instructor or student(s) regarding ethnicity, gender, or sexual orientation, immediately contact: James Morales, Vice President of Student Services, (435) 797-1712, <a href="mailto:james.morales@usu.edu">james.morales@usu.edu</a>. Learn your student rights by visiting: <a href="http://www.usu.edu/studentservices/studentcode/" target="_blank"><u>http://www.usu.edu/studentservices/studentcode</u></a>. (1A; 2A; 3B)</p>
